-not-let-hamas-murderous-barbarism-poison-our-souls/0000018b-f3c2-d117-abcf-f7ef7f620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 23:07:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-must-not-let-hamas-murderous-barbarism-poison-our-souls/0000018b-f3c2-d117-abcf-f7ef7f620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡知道。内塔尼亚胡置若罔闻。内塔尼亚胡负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-knew-netanyahu-ignored-netanyahu-is-responsible/0000018b-f3bf-d117-abcf-f7ff45870000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 22:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-knew-netanyahu-ignored-netanyahu-is-responsible/0000018b-f3bf-d117-abcf-f7ff45870000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡看来，军事情报部门正在抓捕他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-netanyahus-mind-military-intelligence-was-out-to-get-him/0000018b-f32f-d117-abcf-f7ef28910000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 21:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-netanyahus-mind-military-intelligence-was-out-to-get-him/0000018b-f32f-d117-abcf-f7ef28910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意放慢加沙战斗以营救被扣为人质的妇女和儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-accepts-a-slowdown-in-gaza-combat-to-rescue-women-and-children-held-hostage/0000018b-f38e-d558-a3eb-f78ff86a0000</link><description>以色列政府预计将批准的协议与上周拒绝的协议类似。从那时起，甘茨和国防官员担心公众对人质家人日益增长的支持可能会影响战斗</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 21:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-accepts-a-slowdown-in-gaza-combat-to-rescue-women-and-children-held-hostage/0000018b-f38e-d558-a3eb-f78ff86a0000</guid></item><item><title>对美国在伊拉克和也门目标的袭击无人回应，拜登被束缚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-hands-tied-as-the-attacks-on-u-s-targets-in-iraq-and-yemen-go-unanswered/0000018b-f339-d558-a3eb-f73f465a0000</link><description>美国遏制袭击不仅仅是出于防止地区战争的愿望。其目的是结束另一场失败的战争并使沙特阿拉伯摆脱胡塞武装的威胁</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 20:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-hands-tied-as-the-attacks-on-u-s-targets-in-iraq-and-yemen-go-unanswered/0000018b-f339-d558-a3eb-f73f465a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙逮捕著名巴勒斯坦裔美国诗人后获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/renowned-palestinian-american-poet-released-after-israel-arrest-in-gaza/0000018b-f320-dcf8-a3db-f7fa2b390000</link><description>加沙裔美国诗人莫萨布·阿布·托哈 (Mosab Abu Toha) 与家人在前往拉法过境点前往美国的途中与其他加沙人一起被捕</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 18:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/renowned-palestinian-american-poet-released-after-israel-arrest-in-gaza/0000018b-f320-dcf8-a3db-f7fa2b390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院的两项判决带有令人震惊的麦卡锡主义气息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-court-decisions-carry-an-alarming-scent-of-mccarthyism/0000018b-f2f0-d117-abcf-f7ff5f4d0000</link><description>以色列公民在利库德集团家外喷漆后仍被拘留，这对那些打算在战争结束后走上街头要求更换政府的群众来说是一个警告信号</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 18:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-court-decisions-carry-an-alarming-scent-of-mccarthyism/0000018b-f2f0-d117-abcf-f7ff5f4d0000</guid></item><item><title>高级塞法迪拉比呼吁犹太学院学生为以色列军队祈祷，赞扬以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/senior-sephardi-rabbis-call-on-yeshiva-students-to-pray-for-israeli-troops-praise-idf/0000018b-f266-d36e-a3cb-f277080e0000</link><description>前首席拉比什洛莫·阿马尔 (Shlomo Amar) 在 10 月 7 日大屠杀后向与哈马斯作战的士兵致敬，并告诉正统派“不断学习并为他们祈祷”。如果他们放弃自己的生命，我们就袖手旁观吗？</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 17:07:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/senior-sephardi-rabbis-call-on-yeshiva-students-to-pray-for-israeli-troops-praise-idf/0000018b-f266-d36e-a3cb-f277080e0000</guid></item><item><title>前人权观察编辑抨击其对以色列的“不平衡”报道：“有毒且重要的时刻”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/ex-human-rights-watch-editor-explains-shocking-indictment-of-politicized-organization/0000018b-f15e-ddc3-afdb-fd5fc3760000</link><description>丹妮尔·哈斯 (Danielle Haas) 在人权非政府组织工作了超过 13 年，她本人是以色列人，她表示人权观察必须扪心自问，在如此危险的时刻，它是否在以色列-巴勒斯坦问题上“发挥了负责任的作用”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 17:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/ex-human-rights-watch-editor-explains-shocking-indictment-of-politicized-organization/0000018b-f15e-ddc3-afdb-fd5fc3760000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷新总统信奉犹太教。但他会“对犹太人有利”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/argentinas-new-president-embraces-judaism-but-will-he-be-good-for-the-jews/0000018b-f199-d117-abcf-f7ffb49e0000</link><description>极右翼自由主义者哈维尔·米雷在讨论经济政策时经常引用《托拉》中的经文。但拉丁美洲最大的犹太社区对他对犹太教的热情和对以色列的支持最终是否会对他们产生积极影响持保留态度</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 16:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/argentinas-new-president-embraces-judaism-but-will-he-be-good-for-the-jews/0000018b-f199-d117-abcf-f7ffb49e0000</guid></item><item><title>在 LGBTQ 里程碑中，以色列国防军在阵亡士兵的墓碑上列出了三名父母</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/in-lgbtq-milestone-idf-lists-three-parents-on-tombstone-for-fallen-soldier/0000018b-f254-da76-abdb-f7dd71680000</link><description>参谋军士。菲尔施泰因的三个父母是在军队里认识的。 Or-Li 和 Michal 已经恋爱了，想要孩子的 Kobi 也加入了帮助他们生孩子的行列，并共同抚养孩子</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 16:21:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/in-lgbtq-milestone-idf-lists-three-parents-on-tombstone-for-fallen-soldier/0000018b-f254-da76-abdb-f7dd71680000</guid></item><item><title>为以色列军队带来愤怒的极端正统派行动内部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/inside-the-ultra-orthodox-operation-to-bring-cholent-to-the-troops/0000018b-ed3a-d4f0-affb-effb18df0000</link><description>随着数十万以色列人进入预备役部队，正统派正在参与为士兵提供食物的巨大努力。背景音乐从吉他演奏到爆炸声，再到布雷斯洛夫·哈西德音乐</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 15:37:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/inside-the-ultra-orthodox-operation-to-bring-cholent-to-the-troops/0000018b-ed3a-d4f0-affb-effb18df0000</guid></item><item><title>这位大屠杀幸存者习惯了在 TikTok 上与否认者作斗争。哈马斯的辩护者打破了他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-21/ty-article-podcast/this-holocaust-survivor-is-used-to-fighting-deniers-on-tiktok-hamas-apologists-broke-him/0000018b-f1ff-d117-abcf-f7fffd9e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 14:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-21/ty-article-podcast/this-holocaust-survivor-is-used-to-fighting-deniers-on-tiktok-hamas-apologists-broke-him/0000018b-f1ff-d117-abcf-f7fffd9e0000</guid></item><item><title>苯丙胺高浓度和反犹太主义：关于哈马斯使用的“伊斯兰国药物”的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/high-on-captagon-and-antisemitism-everything-about-the-isis-drug-used-by-hamas/0000018b-f230-d558-a3eb-f73face80000</link><description>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件发生后，有报道称恐怖分子服用了兴奋剂苯丙胺，这种药物用于提高表现和减少抑制。这种毒品主要产自叙利亚，被称为“穷人的可卡因”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 14:46:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/high-on-captagon-and-antisemitism-everything-about-the-isis-drug-used-by-h